  id: wfo_we_low_25
  displayName: One Secure Highway
  description: It is time to move our field agents into the enemy's defense headquarters
    zone. According to our field reconnaissance and intelligence reports, only one
    of the exiting routes is secure, and only during specific hours. Therefore, having
    all agents depart and enter the zone simultaneously poses a high risk. Agents
    must use that specific route only and enter the city at designated time intervals.
    Your mission is to coordinate the entry of the agents and provide the necessary
    funding.
