  - displayName: Take the Initiative
    description: Take the initiative and do not relay the orders exactly as told,
      so you can return to your grief-stricken wife as quickly as possible. Instruct
      the agents to use multiple routes and depart at nearly the same time to accelerate
      their entry into the city. Also, provide the agents with under-the-table bonuses
      to keep them motivated for this high-risk operation.
